VIM:

NeoVim game vimbegood 

4 Important Modes: 
1 - Normal, where you start 
2 - Insert, you can move your curser around
3 - Visual, line mode like highlighting with your curser
4 - Command, type commands (:w enter saves the file, :q quites)


Normal Mode: 
J - go up 
K - go down 
L - go left 
H - go right 
W - hops over by word
B - hops backwards

Relative line numbers and counts 


Command Mode 
d - delete (dd delete a line)
u  -undo 
ctrl r - redo the previous action
ctrl u - undo  

Insert 




